                <h1>N.C. Republicans may propose court-packing bill to keep control of state supreme court</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/41705c30-6a96-4955-83f2-1fb607a4be5e.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

